	<div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="https://dealbook.nytimes.com/2014/05/09/morning-agenda-apples-new-tune/" data-title="Apple&#8217;s New Tune" data-description="Apple is said to be in talks to buy Beats Electronics for $3.2 billion. | Ad agencies call off their $35 billion merger. | Companies are weighing moving abroad to escape the United States corporate tax rate. | Timothy F. Geithner wants to be understood.">
